@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5ddcff, #00a1cb, #007acc);
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body > footer {
        background: white;
    }

    .privacy-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .privacy-container h1,
    .privacy-container h2 {
        color: #005f8d;
    }

    .privacy-container ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .contact-box {
        background-color: #f2f9fc;
        padding: 20px;
        border-left: 4px solid #005f8d;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }
</style>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>At <strong>Usal Clinic</strong>, your privacy is a top priority. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal and medical information when you visit our clinic or interact with our services.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> Name, contact info, date of birth, ID numbers.</li>
        <li><strong>Medical Data:</strong> History, diagnosis, treatment plans, prescriptions.</li>
        <li><strong>Appointments & Billing:</strong> Visit logs, insurance details, payment data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Deliver high-quality healthcare services</li>
        <li>Manage appointment scheduling and communication</li>
        <li>Process billing and insurance claims</li>
        <li>Ensure legal and medical compliance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We use secure digital systems, encrypted records, and controlled access to protect your data from unauthorized access or misuse.</p>

    <h2>4. Sharing Information</h2>
    <p>We never sell or rent your personal data. We may share information only with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Medical professionals directly involved in your treatment</li>
        <li>Insurance and billing agencies with your consent</li>
        <li>Government authorities when legally required</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal health records</li>
        <li>Request corrections to inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion, subject to medical/legal limitations</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="contact-box">
        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or privacy concerns, please contact us at:</p>
        <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> usalclinic@hotmail.com<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +961 01 456 102<br />
            <strong>Address:</strong> USAL - Old Airport Road, Ghobeiry
        </p>
        <p><em>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Please check this page periodically.</em></p>
    </div>
</div>
